@startuml
[*] --> PowerOnCheck
PowerOnCheck --> Stop : problem during startup
PowerOnCheck --> Ready : everything fine

Ready --> [*]
Ready --> Ready : reset
Ready --> Monitoring : activate
Ready --> Stop : turn off

Monitoring --> Alarm : sensor triggered
Monitoring --> Monitoring : false alarm or time ends

Alarm --> Normal : password entered
Alarm --> Monitoring : continue monitoring after false alarm

Stop --> [*] : system stops
@enduml
